	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Heri sub cenam eas literas ab <persName type="auto_name">Hosero</persName> accepi, quarum nudius quartus mentio fiebat in alteris, quas per <persName type="auto_name">Leonardum</persName> ad me dedit; coniunctę vero illis erant item tibi inscriptę, quas ab optimo <persName type="auto_name">Linero</persName> iam accipies.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Simul autem advenerat heri <persName type="auto_name">Wonlichius</persName> noster istinc veniens et literarum fasciculum <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentorato</placeName> ab <persName type="auto_name">Huberto</persName> et filio meo adferens.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scribunt autem de rebus <placeName type="auto_name">Gallię</placeName>, mittunt etiam libellum cum <persName type="auto_name">Iohannis Sturmii</persName> praefatione continentem quatuor scripta eucharistica Buceri nostri; pariter novos motus <placeName ref="l492" cert="high">Argentoratenses</placeName> significant.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quę omnia nisi certo mihi perusaderem a <persName type="auto_name">Stuckio</persName> vestro ad te quoque missa, partem aliquam nunc etiam non lectam ad te perferri curassem.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Fac igitur sciam, si quid forte horum desideras.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Non possum quicquam praeterea; ita simul multa mihi scribenda vehementer me urgent.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Bene vale, mi venerande charissimeque Bullingere.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto">12. aprilis.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName ref="p8055" cert="high">A[mbrosius] Bl[aurerus]</persName> t[uus].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="la" type="auto">D. Heinricho Bullingero, venerando et charissimo fratri suo.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
		</body>
	</text>
